---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="$1,500 AI Savings Challenge | Scott Armbruster" description="Test whether your current workflows can generate $1,500 per month in AI-driven savings. Input your tasks and see the potential.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-4 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">
        Interactive Tool
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        $1,500 AI Savings Challenge
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-2">
        Can your workflows generate $1,500/month in AI savings? Input your repetitive tasks and time spent to find out. Most businesses hit the target faster than they think.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-800">
        <iframe
          src="https://calculators-production-1a41.up.railway.app/calculators/savings-challenge?embed=true"
          title="$1,500 AI Savings Challenge"
          class="w-full border-0 h-[600px] sm:h-[800px] md:h-[1000px] lg:h-[2400px]"
          style="background: #0f172a;"
          scrolling="auto"
          loading="lazy"
          allow="clipboard-write"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 mt-4">
        All calculations run in your browser. No data is sent to any server.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Hit the $1,500 Target? Let's Make It Real.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">
        You've identified the savings potential. Now let's build the automations to capture it. I'll help you prioritize and implement the highest-impact workflows first.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/agency"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          View Agency Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          Book a Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
